OL,6,FFormer ITV Calendar presenter Roger
OL,7,FGreenwood has died at the age of 75,
OL,8,Fhis family have said.
OL,10,FGreenwood worked for Yorkshire
OL,11,FTelevision from 1974 to 1989, as a
OL,12,Freporter and newsreader.
OL,14,FHe worked alongside well-known
OL,15,Fcolleagues including Richard Whiteley,
OL,16,FGeoff Druett, Marylyn Webb and Alan
OL,17,FHardwick.
