OL,6,FHis son Jonathan said: "He was very
OL,7,Fpopular with viewers across the region
OL,8,Fand was known for his warmth, his
OL,9,Fsmile and his good humour.
OL,11,F"His kind nature shone through when
OL,12,Fcovering human-interest stories, and
OL,13,Fhis special way of engaging with
OL,14,Fchildren and their families was
OL,15,Fevident in projects such as the 1989
OL,16,FCalendar Christmas Toy Appeal."
