OL,6,FA keen sports fan, Greenwood presented
OL,7,Fthe Calendar Summer Sport series
OL,8,Falongside John Helm. He became close
OL,9,Fto sporting greats including Lord
OL,10,FSebastian Coe, cyclist Beryl Burton,
OL,11,Fboxer Herol "Bomber" Graham, athlete
OL,12,FPeter Elliott and swimmer Adrian
OL,13,FMoorhouse.
OL,15,FOff screen he was an enthusiastic
OL,16,Frunner, completing the Yorkshire Three
OL,17,FPeaks fell race in 1976.
