OL,3,CFormer reporter and newsreader Roger
OL,4,CGreenwood dies aged 75
OL,6,FAfter leaving YTV in 1989, Greenwood
OL,7,Fwent into partnership with his friend
OL,8,Fand colleague Derek Goodall, to form
OL,9,FGoodwood Productions and continued to
OL,10,Fmake corporate and broadcast
OL,11,Ftelevision around the world.
OL,13,FHe died following a battle with cancer.
OL,15,FGreenwood is survived by wife, Susan,
OL,16,Fhis three sons Andrew, Jonathan and
OL,17,FDavid and four grandsons.
